      "contents": "Definition NaiveNondepFunext_implies_Funext@{i j max}\n  : NaiveNondepFunext@{i max max} -> Funext_type@{i j max}\n  := WeakFunext_implies_Funext o NaiveNondepFunext_implies_WeakFunext.",
